text: Sofía Abigaíl Marrero Moreira (born 2000) is a Uruguayan model and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Miss Uruguay 2018 and represented Uruguay at the Miss Universe 2018 pageant in Bangkok, Thailand. ==Pageantry== ===Miss Uruguay 2018=== Sofía Marrero from Montevideo was crowned as Miss Uruguay 2018 on 28 August 2018. She succeeded outgoing Miss Uruguay 2017, Marisol Acosta. ===Miss Universe 2018=== As Miss Uruguay, Marrero represented Uruguay at Miss Universe 2018 in Bangkok, Thailand. ==References== ==External links== *Official Miss Uruguay website Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Miss Universe 2018 contestants Category:Uruguayan beauty pageant winners Category:Uruguayan female models Category:People from Montevideo
